title: Linen 'n Things USA Store Locations 12.2007
name: Linen 'n Things USA Store Locations 12.2007
description:
Linen 'n Things is a retailer of home textiles, housewares, and decorative home accessories in the United States and Canada. They have their headquarters in Clifton, New Jersey and were started in 1995.

This dataset displays all the Linen 'n Things store locations across the United States. The dataset contains the store's physical address and lat/lon coordinates. Addresses were obtained from lnt.com and are current as of 12.2007. Addresses were geocoded to obtain their lat/lon coordinates.

For more information, go to lnt.com

Data accessed on December 19, 2007

http://www.lnt.com/corp/index.jsp?page=storeLocator&clickid=topnav_storeloc_txt
